elements.name: Booking Through New Walk In Flow

steps.name: User Login to NBI application with Username and Password
User navigates to Admin Portal page
User click on Venue Name "My Pizza Shop"
User click on open Restaurant button
User should see the Booking page displaying
User click on New Walk In button
User select table option is "T1"
User click on Customer Walk in tab and input Name is "Joes"
User input Booking note is "Test"
User click on Save button
User open created booking with name is "Joes"
Users should see that the information they have entered is displayed correctly
User cancel above booking
